%% @mentions in group chats — send + notify flow
%% Design: docs/design/T2-group-mentions.md · ADR-0008
%% Flag: muhabbet.mentions.enabled / MentionsConfig.ENABLED (default OFF)
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Sender
    participant Composer as Mobile Composer
    participant WS as ChatWebSocketHandler
    participant Svc as MessageService
    participant MRepo as MentionRepository
    participant Notifier as MentionNotifier
    participant Push as PushNotificationPort (FCM)
    participant Members as Group members (WS)

    Sender->>Composer: type "@"
    Composer->>Composer: show roster autocomplete (local group members)
    Sender->>Composer: pick "Ayşe" → insert highlighted token
    Composer->>WS: SendMessage{content, mentions:[{U2,8,5}], mentionsEveryone:false}

    alt flag OFF
        WS->>Svc: sendMessage (mentions ignored → empty)
        Note over Svc: byte-identical to today
    else flag ON
        WS->>Svc: sendMessage(command + mentions)
        Svc->>Svc: validate each mention.userId ∈ conversation_members (drop non-members)
        opt mentionsEveryone
            Svc->>Svc: require sender ADMIN/OWNER else MSG_MENTION_EVERYONE_FORBIDDEN
            Svc->>Svc: expand to all memberIds (cap everyoneMaxMembers)
        end
        Svc->>MRepo: persist message + message_mentions rows
        Svc-->>WS: ServerAck(OK)
        Svc->>Members: broadcast NewMessage{...mentions...}
        Svc->>Notifier: notifyMentioned(message, mentionedIds)
        loop each mentioned member
            alt online & convo not muted
                Note over Notifier: already saw NewMessage → no push
            else offline OR convo muted
                Notifier->>Notifier: skip if globally-muted or blocked sender
                Notifier->>Push: send("Ayşe mentioned you in <group>")
            end
        end
    end
